	* src/PlayerInterface.cs (ImportWithFileSelector,
	OnMenuImportFilesActivate): 
	* src/Preferences.cs (OnButtonLibraryChangeClicked): Remove
	incorrect (but harmless) "gnome-vfs" arg.

