2005-08-30  Dan Winship  <danw@novell.com>

	* Makefile.am (SUBDIRS): add po/

	* mediaengines/gst/GstPlayerEngine.cs: 
	* mediaengines/gst/gst-encode.c: 
	* mediaengines/gst/gst-player-engine.c: 
